{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Add fades/ramps at time selection edges on chosen envelopes (Ducking)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Creates a ducked section \u175 ?\u175 ?____/\u175 ?\u175 ? in the time selection. Inserts points at time selection edges. Works on selected envelope or selected tracks envelope with armed visible envelope.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Configurable values - either in the pop-up prompt or in the script:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab length, shape and depth of left ramp\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab length, shape and depth of right ramp\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab portion of each ramp in % that will be outside of the time selection. E.g. if the left fade is 2 seconds long and the portion outside of the time selection is set to 50%, the fade will begin 1 second before the time selection.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Known issue: mix of envelopes with fader and amplitude scaling causes wrong values\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Setup\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\i optional} deactivate the pop up windows in Basic Settings section in script\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\i optional} set default values for one or multiple envelope types in script\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Usage\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab create time selection\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab select an envelope\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab execute the script\sa180\par}
